Hello Sasha,

Thank you for your prompt response. I am a fiduciary agent to an asset
management and finance firm based in London,  united kingdom.
(www.centturioncapital.com )

 We are seeking a long term investment partnership with an impressive
ROI on investor share value.

If interested, do send me the following to enable me forward to the
management for a detailed review.

1. Name in full
2. Name of registered
    company and your
    position in the company.
3. Amount of financing
    requesting for.
4. Country of origin
5. Mobile telephone number.

Regards,

James
